@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@userId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@organizationId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Healthcheck (Postgres + Mongo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Listar organizations
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizations
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

### Criar organization
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizations
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
x-user-id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "12341",
  "name": "Holding Principal",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Editar organization
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/organizations/{{organizationId}}
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
x-user-id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Holding Principal (Editada)",
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### Remover organization (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/organizations/{{organizationId}}
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
x-user-id: {{userId}}

### Criar item (Postgres + AuditLog em Mongo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Item de teste"
}

### Listar itens (Postgres)
GET {{baseUrl}}/items
